BubbleSetLayout
public class BubbleSetLayout.BubbleSetLabelLayout
extends prefuse.action.ItemAction

Positions aggregate labels (DecoratorItems) along the longest virtual edge in the aggregate. Rotates label up to +-45 degress to follow the edge. Label size is modulated to fit within the length of the edge.
